name: Rosewood Newborn Bonnet
description:
Our Rosewood Bonnet is a combination of lace, pearls, and linens to create a sweet whimsical vintage look for newborn photos. The perfect little layers around your little loves head. 

Bonnets look best when tied snug around your little ones head, with the back synched to fit. Tie in a bow, or leave long and flowing.
